StoredProcedureOraclev10g.name: GETSTAFF
StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.GETSTAFF(cStaff OUT SYS_REFCURSOR)&lt;br/&gt;IS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; OPEN cStaff FOR &lt;br/&gt; SELECT Staff_table.idPerson, Staff_table.surname, Staff_table.firstName, &lt;br/&gt; Staff_table.title, Staff_table.address, Staff_table.phone, Staff_table.postcode,&lt;br/&gt; Staff_table.campusLocation, Staff_table.idBuilding, Staff_table.numberOffice , Staff_table.staffType&lt;br/&gt; FROM Staff_table;&lt;br/&gt;END getStaff;
